(7, 'managed-dedicated-servers-in-india', 'Web Werks Dedicated Server Hosting in India', 'bc2b0d42d02779ff727a5632f.jpeg', '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks Dedicated Server Hosting in India</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>With Web Werks Value for money servers or High-performance dedicated servers allow customers to have complete control over their servers, including choice of Operating System, Hardware etc. Our Redundant Network Infrastructure makes us the most stable and reliable <a class="bold" href="https://www.webwerks.in/data-centers-in-india/">data center service provider</a> in India and in the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our dedicated servers support Windows and Linux OS platform with 24&times;7 Rapid Action Technical Support. To ease your understanding of the right selection of servers as per your requirement, you can select from our wide range of unmanaged and managed dedicated hosting options.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<div class="accordion">\r\n<section id="one">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Operating System</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Variations of Linux included CentOS, Fedora Core, Debian and many other Linux distributions such as BSD systems FreeBSD, NetBSD, OpenBSD. Our other Operating System offering includes Microsoft windows server 2008 &ndash; 2012 edition, which is provided through a special program called Microsoft Service Provider License Agreement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What other features are included along with our OS offering on dedicated web servers?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>O/S Design &amp; Implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Hardening &amp; Performance Management</li>\r\n	<li>Service Monitoring Tools</li>\r\n	<li>High-Availability Server (Cluster) Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="two">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Support</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks offers 24&times;7 Rapid Action Support bundled with our server hosting service offerings. We broadly scale from Unmanaged Services to Managed Services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>What does Web Werks Server Management Services include?</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WW Infra Management: &ndash; A support team dedicated to your needs from operating system, patches and security updates.</li>\r\n	<li>Compute Management: &ndash; To ensure, your applications; databases and your online presence are always up and running with robust Network, CPU, RAM and disk I/O performance.</li>\r\n	<li>RA Priority Upgrades: &ndash; <strong>Rapid Action Support</strong> to Processor, RAM, Hard Disk(s) and OS level upgrades.</li>\r\n	<li>Service Level Upgrades: &ndash; Mission-Critical Application Upgrades, Scheduled Database Upgrades and Guidelines Support are included.</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Firewall Support: &ndash; Dedicated Cisco ASA Firewall Management with additional security tweaks to ensure your business is safe from all external and potential threats.</li>\r\n	<li>Risk Management: &ndash; We keep your servers risk-free, so you don&rsquo;t need to worry about your business continuity. Our guidelines are deployed on your servers to ensure you never face a downtime. A further support with Service Level Agreement is offered.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Let&rsquo;s say, I want to go with Unmanaged Services, what do you offer?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Unmanaged Services with our dedicated servers includes the following:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Basic server setup</li>\r\n	<li>OS Installations</li>\r\n	<li>Control Panel Installations (If, Required)</li>\r\n	<li>Hardware, Network and Server Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>99.9% Guaranteed Uptime SLA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="three">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Security</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>At Web Werks, highest Security measures are taken to ensure the safety of data stored on our network of servers. We deploy various software programs for scanning systems and networks for obtrusive invaders, spammers, hackers, and other harmful problems such as Trojans, worms, eggdrops and crashers (Sending multiple connections). Linux and Windows use different software for security protection.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Security design &amp; implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Data security Management</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Firewall Management</li>\r\n	<li>Intrusion detection and Intrusion Prevention system</li>\r\n	<li>Virus and Malware Scanning and Filtering</li>\r\n	<li>Installation of Advanced Policy Firewall</li>\r\n	<li>SSL Cert Guidelines (Optional, <strong>Secured Socket Layer Services</strong>)</li>\r\n	<li>Threat Alert Management</li>\r\n	<li>DDoS Mitigation (For more details, please contact our <strong><a href="http://www.webwerks.in/support/">Support Team</a></strong>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="four">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Control Panel</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Control Panel software is an all-inclusive set of software applications, server applications, and automation tools that can be installed on your dedicated servers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Control panels include integration into web servers, database applications, programming languages, application deployment, server administration tasks, and include the ability to automate tasks via a web based front end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer the following Control Panels on our servers: -</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On Linux OS Servers: &ndash; <strong>cPanel / WHM Control Panel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Unlimited Domain, Email and FTP Management</li>\r\n	<li>Installed Application Version Management</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-Application Deployment &ndash; Over 200+ Applications</li>\r\n	<li>Email, Instant Messaging or SMS Notifications for service restarts</li>\r\n	<li>Security Settings Enabler</li>\r\n	<li>Software Updates and Fix</li>\r\n	<li>Password-Protect Directories</li>\r\n	<li>Website Traffic Analyzer and much more.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>On Windows OS Servers :- <strong>Plesk Control Panel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Account and Reseller Management</li>\r\n	<li>Domain License and Unlimited Email Support</li>\r\n	<li>PgSQL, MSSQL, Tomcat, ColdFusion Support</li>\r\n	<li>iPhone &amp; Android devices Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Security Core* with ModSecurity &nbsp;Rules by Atomicorp</li>\r\n	<li>ServerShield&trade; by CloudFlare</li>\r\n	<li>Outbound Antispam</li>\r\n	<li>Email Antivirus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Security design &amp; implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Data security Management</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Firewall Management</li>\r\n	<li>Intrusion detection and Intrusion Prevention system</li>\r\n	<li>Virus and Malware Scanning and Filtering</li>\r\n	<li>Installation of Advanced Policy Firewall</li>\r\n	<li>SSL Cert Guidelines (Optional, <strong>Secured Socket Layer Services</strong>)</li>\r\n	<li>Threat Alert Management</li>\r\n	<li>DDoS Mitigation (For more details, please contact our <strong><a href="http://www.webwerks.in/support/">Support Team</a></strong>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection ">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Web Werks Dedicated Hosting Specifications</h2>\r\n<img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Web Werks Dedicated Server Hosting in India', '', '', 1, '2014-12-25 12:27:36', '2014-12-25 13:21:46'),
(8, 'budget-dedicated-hosting-plans-in-india', 'Budget Servers', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Budget <span>Servers</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are low on budget, no problem &ndash; web werks has a server solution for you. Our Value for money dedicated hosting plans is designed to suit your pocket without compromising the quality performance which has always been a part of Web Werks Commitment to its customers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Budget Servers', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 12:59:08', '2014-12-25 13:26:33'),
(9, 'power-web-server-plans', 'Power Servers', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Power <span>Servers</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Our next range of servers with a little upgrade of hardware resources. These are the best match to you if your business is growing and you don&rsquo;t wish to move to Enterprise dedicated hosting with high-end specifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our power server ranges are upgrades from basic Dual core to Quad Core configurations with RAM up to 16GB RAM; 2 x 1TB drives or above with support to Linux and Windows Operating Systems.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Power Servers', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 13:29:00', '2014-12-25 13:29:00'),
(10, 'enterprise-dedicated-hosting-plans', 'Enterprise Servers', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Enterprise <span>Servers</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Enterprise ranges of servers are best fit to Enterprise Organizations; heavy resource intensive e-Commerce websites or Mission-Critical Business Applications. These server ranges from Dual Quad Core to Dual Hexa Processors with support up to 128GB RAM and multiple drives slots for more storage space on the servers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Web Werks, we also help you to setup high-configuration Server Clusters with options to Disaster Recovery in five different geographical <strong><a href="http://www.webwerks.in/data-centers-in-india/">data center</a></strong>locations.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Enterprise Servers', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 13:31:11', '2014-12-25 13:31:11'),
(11, 'vps-hosting-in-india', 'Web Werks VPS Hosting', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks<br />\r\n<span>VPS Hosting</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks virtual private hosting gives you complete access over your server environment at only a fraction of a cost to that of a dedicated server with endless functionalities of a control panel, Mail Servers, Managed backup and Firewall. We help you to setup your virtual servers on various operating systems which are Linux (CentOS, Fedora, Debian) and Windows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our VPS Hosting Servers are managed by our high-quality technical support and of course competitive pricing. At Web Werks, we understand our customer needs to achieve their IT goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks services cater to all businesses from small; medium to Enterprise and enables companies to work faster; smarter and with more flexibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Run high usage applications and the multiple websites</li>\r\n	<li>Get your server online in minutes with free instant set up</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible payment options to suit any budget</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection ">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Why Choose Web Werks as your VPS Hosting Provider ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stable and Reliable Setup on VMware Virtualization Platform with some of the features mentioned below :-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Rapidly scalable resources with on-demand dedicated CPU.</li>\r\n	<li>Keep your critical applications up and running with high performance, high availability servers.</li>\r\n	<li>Benefit from high-availability servers deployed on redundant server clusters and redundant enterprise class storage.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>VPS Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list"