(13, 'enterprise-vps-servers-in-india', 'Enterprise VPS Plans', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Enterprise VPS Plans</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks offers High-end Power VPS Servers with capability up to 8 Virtual Cores, 400GB Storage and 500GB Bandwidth per month. The way we have built them is to support your high-end business needs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n                        	<h2>VPS Benefits</h2>\r\n                            <ul class="benefits-list">\r\n                            <li> <strong>We Own our Data Centers:  </strong> At Web Werks, we own our data centers which are managed by our own 24Ã—7 On-site Engineers. Your business is always safe with us. </li>\r\n                            <li> <strong> Reliability:</strong> Our network is backed by a 99.995% Uptime Guarantee policy with 24Ã—7 access to our expert technical support representatives via Phone and Email.</li>\r\n                            <li> <strong>Reduced Cost: </strong> Only pay for the requirement that you need by dialing in your CPU/RAM requirements and avoid paying for resources that you will not use.</li>\r\n                            <li> <strong>High Performance: </strong> Improve your business performance with our automated load-balancing technology for VPS. It assesses the resources needed by your VPS and distributes workloads across physical available machines to gives you the best performance from your VPS.</li>\r\n                            <li> <strong>Root/ Admin Full Access: </strong> Offering full root access, which means that you can easily install advanced software and completely customize virtually as if your account were a dedicated server. With the full root access feature, usual administration can be done through the cPanel which is one of the most user-friendly control panels today.</li>\r\n                            \r\n                          </ul>\r\n                        </div>\r\n<div class="benefits-block">\r\n                        	<h2>Why Web Werks ?</h2>\r\n                            <ul class="benefits-list">\r\n                            <li>Enterprise Virtual Servers</li>\r\n                            <li>High-Performance Setup</li>\r\n                            <li>Ease-Upgrade Process</li>\r\n                            <li>Ready Deployment</li>\r\n                            <li>No Setup Fee</li>\r\n\r\n                          </ul>\r\n                        </div>', 'Enterprise VPS Plans', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 13:50:06', '2014-12-25 13:50:06'),
(14, 'cloud-servers-in-india', 'Web Werks Cloud Hosting Services', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks<br />\r\n<span>Cloud Hosting Services</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks cloud hosting servers are designed keeping your IT requirements in mind to give you improved ROI with ultimate flexibility and data assurance. Our Proven, tested and trustworthy approach will help you in determining the business drivers and components with understanding of deployment in a Private or Public Cloud Environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can choose from our extensive range of solutions, some to mention are :-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="inner-list clearfix">\r\n	<li>Public and Private Cloud Hosting (Generic Cloud Offerings)</li>\r\n	<li>Cloud Email Solutions (Hosted for variety of Email Platforms)</li>\r\n	<li>Cloud Storage (Specifically designed for increased space management at a lower cost)</li>\r\n	<li>Cloud Load-balancers (Intelligent distribution over multiple servers)</li>\r\n	<li>Database Cloud Services (Designed for manage heavy-resource intensive databases)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Cloud provides you the freedom to choose from Public, Private, Managed and Unmanaged cloud Options.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Cloud Plaform Options</h2>\r\n<img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<div class="accordion">\r\n<section id="one">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">VCCIM</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks&rsquo;s Customer Isolation Module has three main functions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Secure VLAN sharing: WCCIM enables secure sharing of VLANs among multiple virtual machines, managing multiple VLANs in the cloud and their assigned IPs</li>\r\n	<li>Private VLANs: with WCCIM client isolation, every user is secure in their own section of the cloud. We gives you the security of a private VLAN system with less overhead.</li>\r\n	<li>WCCIM firewall: WCCIM provides an additional layer of firewall security on hypervisors (see below).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="two">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Security</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks Cloud has a Multi-layered security model. It enables cloud providers and their customers to customize security measures at the network, hypervisor and virtual machine layer.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="three">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Virtualization Approach</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks Cloud&rsquo;s server hardware virtualization architecture provides the foundation for a secure cloud service, by maintaining isolation of virtual machine and hypervisor operating systems. This approach is more reliable in a hosted cloud than, for example, container-based virtualization, where virtual machines and hosts share core OS components. In an Web Werks cloud, any attack on the host OS has no direct effect on client virtual machines.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="four">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Firewall Security</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks cloud platform has four layers of firewall protection. This includes firewalls on the network, firewalls on hypervisors and firewalls on individual virtual machines. This may, of course, be extended with additional hardware/software firewall at the network infrastructure, hypervisor and virtual machine layer.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Network / infrastructure firewalls:</strong> hardware firewalls built into the cloud host&rsquo;s network infrastructure / data center infrastructure.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Hypervisor firewalls: </strong> Web Werks Cloud Hosting Infrastructure makes full use of all security features built into supported Hypervisor platforms to maintain complete isolation of virtual machines and their Data.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>WCCIM firewalls: </strong> It also features proprietary firewall technology built into hypervisors as part of the WCCIM module. This provides additional anti-spoofing and anti-sniffing protection to ensure VMs cannot interact with other VMs&rsquo; data, except where explicitly allowed. The firewall examine packets entering and leaving virtual machines, blocks any that do not meet rules set by the Web Werks Controller server.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Virtual machine firewalls: </strong> the final layer is an end-user firewall that is configurable on each individual virtual machine. Each VM can be configured to accept or drop traffic from specified IPs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="five">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Security VM templates</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks virtual machine templates can easily be configured with dedicated security technologies, such as Gazzang encryption. By incorporating additional security technologies into virtual machines, cloud hosts (and their customers) can easily configure virtual machines to support additional security and compliance requirements, such as PCI.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id="five">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Permissions Engine</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Detailed permissions engine offers a further level of security. Every function in our cloud can be enabled or disabled for any user on-demand. This can be used to prevent unauthorized users from modifying hypervisor, network, data store and other sensitive elements of the cloud, as well as more fundamental tasks such as preventing one user from seeing another user&rsquo;s virtual machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>High Performance </strong> Web Werks cloud is optimized across the stack for high performance &mdash; from premium hardware to custom performance enhancing technologies and meeting your requirements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Global Footprint </strong> Choose where your data and applications reside. Build and manage across 5 data centers in the US and India.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Enterprise-Level Security </strong> Your data on Web Werks Cloud are protected by keeping your business and its confidentiality in mind. 6 Zone Enterprise level security keeps your data safe and secure.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Disaster Recovery </strong> Built-in disaster recovery solutions reinforce our highly redundant infrastructure and provides you with peace of mind.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>High Availability </strong> Web Werks Cloud includes powerful load balancing and redundancy features that improve Uptime and keeps your websites up and running.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Web Werks Cloud Hosting Services', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:08:42', '2014-12-25 14:08:42'),
(15, 'public-cloud-hosting-in-india', 'Public Cloud Solutions', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Public Cloud <span>Solutions</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Public Cloud provides you scalability, robustness, high availability and control for your IT Infrastructure and improves your ROI and bring down your IT Expenditures. Even when your Requirement is for a single server or a robust high availability solution we have the Cloud hosting solution that meets your requirement at prices that&rsquo;s calculated in hourly or monthly basis.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection"><img src="/theme/webwerks//img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Public Cloud Solutions', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:10:49', '2014-12-25 14:10:49'),
(16, 'private-cloud-in-india', 'Web Werks Private Cloud Servers', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks Private Cloud Servers</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Private Cloud provides you with dedicated resources and complete control over the cloud with choices of OS, Applications and scalability over your dedicated cloud. Private cloud also enables you to deploy more instances and conducting maintenance remotely with complete control.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm "><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Web Werks Private Cloud Servers', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:17:05', '2014-12-25 14:17:05'),
(17, 'smart-cloud-solutions-plans', 'Smart Cloud Plans', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Smart Cloud <span>Plans</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Web Werks Smart cloud</strong> is where dedicated hosting meets the cloud as it allows users to</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Allocate hypervisors on a 1:1 basis: each customer gets a dedicated hypervisor for their hosted service</li>\r\n	<li>Failover is provided by the rest of the cloud (for example, one HV might act as failover for 5 &ldquo;live&rdquo; HVs)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optimize your IT Infrastructure and Improve ROI using Web Werks Cloud Solutions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gone those days of force fitting your hosting requirement from the available resources, Web Werks Cloud Solutions is designed keeping your IT requirements in mind to give you improved ROI with ultimate flexibility and data assurance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Proven, Tested and trustworthy approach will help your in determining the business drivers and components. This will help you in understanding what component should move into private or public cloud.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Cloud provides you the freedom to choose from Public, Private, Managed and Unmanaged cloud Options.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Smart Cloud Plans', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:19:32', '2014-12-25 14:19:32'),
(18, 'data-center-in-pune', 'Internet Data Center in Pune', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Internet Data Center<br />\r\n<span>in Pune</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Over the past decade Web-Werks has created a robust and stable network. Our data center in pune is third in India and 5th overall after Mumbai, Navi Mumbai, Philadelphia and Conshohocken . Its Web- Werks first strategic location within Pune, a city with one of the fastest growing populations of Internet users. Web-Werks, Having state of the art Tier 3 Internet Data Centers located in Hinjewadi, Pune. Data center has precision-controlled air conditions systems with incorporated redundancy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide 24&times;7 power back up systems for all the equipments to ensure zero downtime or minimal interruptions in operations due to high capacity, power cut, reliable power generators. sophisticated onsite security through surveillance cameras and advanced biometric systems to prevent unlawful entry networking equipments are fully redundant high-end switches and routers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<div class="datacenter_sliders">\r\n<div class="flexslider dc_gallery" id="slider">\r\n<div class="flex-viewport" style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; height: 286px;">\r\n<ul class="slides" style="width: 1600%; transition-duration: 0s; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);">\r\n	<li class="flex-active-slide" style="width: 697px; float: left; display: block;"><img alt="" draggable="false" src="/theme/webwerks/img/gallery/img1.jpg" /></li>\r\n	<li style="width: 697px; float: left; display: block;"><img draggable="false" src="/theme/webwerks/img/gallery/img2.jpg" /></li>\r\n	<li style="width: 697px; float: left; display: block;"><img draggable="false" src="/theme/webwerks/img/gallery/Pune-datacenter1.jpg" /></li>\r\n	<li style="width: 697px; float: left; display: block;"><img draggable="false" src="/theme/web