(19, 'mumbai-dc-facility', 'Data Center Services in Mumbai', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Data Center Services<br />\r\n<span>in Mumbai</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Data Center is located in the heart of Mumbai, Prabhadevi which is ideal for hosting business in the emerging market with premium high-speed internet connectivity from multiple Internet Service Providers including Airtel, MTNL, TTSL, TTML and Sify.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our commitment towards delivering to our customers has always been par excellence. Mumbai which is known to be an Alpha World City is where we have built our Data Center and offer wide range of web hosting services including VPS Hosting, Colocation Services and Dedicated Servers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">One Web Werks Navi Mumbai Data Center</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>After a phenomenal success of our data center in Mumbai &ndash; Prabhadevi, we now have come up with our latest data center facility in Navi Mumbai. Keeping our consistent N+1 redundancy feature in mind, we now have deployed more rack space to serve more customers from Small to Enterprise businesses. Upgraded Network, Cooling and Power Backup solutions are now a premium feature of our new facility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High-performance and latest dedicated server hosting configurations have been deployed at this facility to ensure our commitment towards our customers are met at all times.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<div class="datacenter_sliders">\r\n<div class="flexslider dc_gallery" id="slider">\r\n<div class="flex-viewport" style="overflow: hidden; position: relative; height: 286px;">\r\n<ul class="slides" style="width: 1600%; transition-duration: 0s; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);">\r\n	<li class="flex-active-slide" style="width: 697px; float: left; display: block;"><img alt="" draggable="false" src="/theme/webwerks/img/gallery/Mumbai-DC-Webwerks