(22, 'colocation-service-providers-in-india', 'Web Werks Colocation Server Hosting in India & US', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks Colocation Server Hosting in India &amp; US</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks offers a wide array of unmanaged and managed Colocation services in 5 different Data Center locations to meet small, medium and large Enterprise Business requirements. Our data center facilities are fully equipped with dual fiber entry points, battery backup, diesel generators, HVAC compressors, fire suppression and Multiple Bandwidth Providers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>24&times;7 On-site Technicians and Engineers are also available to assist customers round the clock. We allow and recommend our customers to visit our data center prior to deployment of their server hardware, this is to assure that we always stick to our commitment and never fall short of it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter what your business is, no matter how many servers you need to colocate, no matter how much bandwidth you need, Web Werks always has an affordable co-location hosting service or a dedicated rack for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For standard requirements or custom requirements, please feel free to contact us for a quote. For business continuity and to decrease IT expenses, there is only one name &ndash; Web Werks India !!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<div class="accordion">\r\n<section id="one">\r\n<h2><a href="javascript:void(0)">Server Colocation</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Web Werks Colocation Services in India and US lets you customize your needs from 1U on up of usable space, securely locked in a world-class data center at 5 locations and phenomenal support to meet your IT needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Single Colo solutions are perfect for the client that has less than a full rack worth of equipment as it helps in avoiding over-investing in cabinet space while providing access to a facility that provi