	<li>24x7x365 Guided Datacenter Access</li>\r\n	<li>24 x 7 Network &amp; Security Monitoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style2">\r\n	<li>Hosting on Secure High Availability Hosting Infrastructure.</li>\r\n	<li>5 Colocation Facility to choose from ( 3 in India and 2 in US)</li>\r\n	<li>Superior Performance, Scalability, Reliability &amp; Connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>Options for backup/recovery and L2 services available</li>\r\n	<li>99.995% Network &amp; Power Uptime SLA</li>\r\n	<li>True 24 x 7 Support with managed services options.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Colo Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Growth Planning of Your Architecture</li>\r\n	<li>We Own the Hardware and All Parts of Hardware Life Cycle Management</li>\r\n	<li>24x7x365 Data Center and Account Management Support</li>\r\n	<li>Tools to Remotely Manage Your Environment</li>\r\n	<li>Highly Secure and Redundant Data Centers and Network</li>\r\n	<li>On-demand Web Werks Managed and Professional Services</li>\r\n	<li>Aggregate Transfer Bandwidth Pricing</li>\r\n	<li>Industry-leading Service Level Agreements around Infrastructure Support</li>\r\n	<li>High Availability Hosting Infrastructure.</li>\r\n	<li>Superior Performance, Scalability, Reliability &amp; Connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>Options for Backup/Recovery and L2; L3 services available</li>\r\n	<li>Rack with specified rated power consumption &ndash; from 2KW to 16KW</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible Data Transfer | Fixed Bandwidth OR Burstable Bandwidth options.</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-Tier Secure Co-location Infrastructure to protect your servers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Web Werks Colocation Server Hosting in India & US', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:55:19', '2014-12-25 14:55:19'),
(23, '2u-5u-12u-colocation-hosting-in-india', 'Web Werks Single Server DC Colocation Service', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks Single Server<br />\r\n<span>DC Colocation Service</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Single Server colocation services ranges from 1U upto 12U usable space. This service is ideal for single server hardware or upto &frac14; of a 42U Rack cabinet depending upon the size of your server hardware. If you have a business running on your server of size (1U) or multiple server clusters upto 12U, our single server DC colocation is the best option for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Webwerks Colocation let you customize your colo needs from 1U on up of usable space, securely locked in a world-class data center at 5 locations and incredible support to meet your IT needs.</li>\r\n	<li>Webwerks Single Colo solutions are perfect for the client that has less than a full rack worth of equipment as it helps in avoiding over-investing in cabinet space while providing access to a facility that provides the highest level of security, reliability and availability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm"><img src="/theme/webwerks/img/range-700.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Complete On-site Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Traffic Volume Management</li>\r\n	<li>Uninterrupted Power Supply</li>\r\n	<li>Deployment Guidance Program</li>\r\n	<li>As per ISO and TIA-942 Standards</li>\r\n	<li>Hosted in Tier 3 and Tier 4 DC Facilities</li>\r\n	<li>Firewall Deployment and Configurations</li>\r\n	<li>Six Layer Security maintained &ndash; 24x7x365</li>\r\n	<li>99.9% Network Guaranteed Uptime SLA</li>\r\n	<li>24&times;7 Rapid Action NOC Support Team</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Web Werks Single Server DC Colocation Service', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:57:35', '2014-12-25 14:59:54'),
(24, '42u-rack-colocation-services-in-india', 'Web Werks Server Rack Colocation Hosting Service', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks Server<br />\r\n<span>Rack Colocation Hosting Service</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Maintaining your own secure, reliable datacenter environment and running your own dedicated lines can be burdensome and costly. With Web Werks Managed Co-location Services, we remove this burden. Save yourself a lot of money and headache by allowing Web Werks to care for your precious hardware and data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data Center Colocation at Web Werks India IDC is an outsourcing solution where the client places their server&rsquo;s &amp; networking gear in our redundant Data Center &ndash; We provide the rackspace, bandwidth, routing, cooling &amp; power.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h4 class="title-inner">Rack Colocation Features</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul class="inner-list">\r\n	<li>Choose from 5 Data Centers</li>\r\n	<li>99.9% Guaranteed Uptime</li>\r\n	<li>Carrier Neutral Data Centers</li>\r\n	<li>Bandwidth on 100Mbps Port</li>\r\n	<li>Redundant Power Supply</li>\r\n	<li>Complete Security Provisioning</li>\r\n	<li>CDN and Firewall Support</li>\r\n	<li>Private Cages Available</li>\r\n	<li>24&times;7 On-site NOC Support Team</li>\r\n	<li>Server and Rack Monitoring Tools</li>\r\n	<li>Online Bandwidth Monitoring Tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li><strong>Cost-efficient: </strong> Power and cooling capabilities are customized for High Density colocation and will ensure that they are managed in a cost effective and in an efficient manner.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Monitoring: </strong> Engineers at Web Werks monitor and manage your high-density hosting environment to ensure that power and cooling conditions are optimized to meet its needs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Resilient: </strong> Web Werks ensures its customers with high-capacity and redundant power supplies, backed up by Diesel generators and UPS.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Secure: </strong> Advanced fire detection/suppression and data center security systems provide very early detection to help avoid fire, loss and business disruption.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>High Density: </strong> Up to 20 kW of cooling capacity per cabinet for high density hosting.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Web Werks Server Rack Colocation Hosting Service', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 14:59:05', '2014-12-25 14:59:05'),
(25, 'managed-email-sql-migration-services-in-india', 'Web Werks Migration Services', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks<br />\r\n<span>Migration Services</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>New capabilities and integrating devices without compromising network availability or performance is critical to success. When you are deploying a new system and need to migrate network services, the challenge is to migrate efficiently while controlling price and mitigating risk that could affect your business or your production infrastructure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data Migration is best undertaken in a comprehensive way with a long-term view, rather than taking a project-by-project refresh approach that leaves the network architecture complex and uneven.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data Migration Services help you by taking priorities, systematic-based approach to refreshing the network infrastructure now and keeping it refreshed into the future. They help you identify business and technical requirements and document the current state of your network infrastructure and business. It helps to guide you through creating a strategy and phased migration plan, and always provide support for migration and implementation, and knowledge transfer throughout the process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Why Web Werks Migration?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Data Center Migration Service helps enterprises and service providers improve business agility, end-user experience, and total cost of ownership with minimal risk, complexity, and resource consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The flexibility of our data migrations tools and our expertise in migration, data migration, data replications and business continuity allow us to optimize service delivery and accommodate a variety requirement. The service will help you benefits from the simpler IT infrastructure, reduced management complexity and lower totals cost ownership.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More effectively manage the migration of new devices, solutions, and applications by gaining continuous insight into the overall state of your network with WEB WERKS service capabilities. These capabilities provide visibility into your infrastructure by automating the analysis of diagnostic network data and relating it with WEB WERKs deep knowledge base. You get the benefit of our 18 years of industry experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Increase efficiency through guidance, quick migration deployment and cutover time and support from experienced team with proven methods of procedures.</li>\r\n	<li>It helps to retain and protects information; it opens the opportunity to utilize information more efficiently and effectively.</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce support problems and system disruption with aggressive plan for replacing declining network components.</li>\r\n	<li>Keep productivity high during migrations.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure state-of-the-art migration techniques that employ experienced professionals, specialized migrations tools, best practiced and proven methodologies</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce or eliminated windows</li>\r\n	<li>Reduces business interruptions during the migrations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Web Werks Migration Services', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:01:41', '2014-12-25 15:01:41'),
(26, 'disaster-recovery-as-a-service-provider-in-india', 'High-Availability DR Service for Business Continuity', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">High-Availability DR Service<br />\r\n<span>for Business Continuity</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes in protecting your data and applications, it&rsquo;s not just about the backup. Being able to rapidly recover your key servers and an application to productions is just as important. Because every minute you&rsquo;re down, you&rsquo;re losing business. The fact is not too many companies don&rsquo;t protect their data. Web Werks Data center disaster recovery as a service is designed to help companies to replicate critical servers and applications to the cloud, so that it can protect the applications and data, and get them back when needed them most. DRaas makes it far more feasible and affordable for companies of all sizes to take advantages of replication and recovery to a secondary environment while gaining the benefits of a managed recovery process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When putting together a Disaster Recovery plan, there are several crucial factors that will need to be considered so that the final DR is as effective as possible; these include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recovery Time Objective (RTO)</strong> &ndash; The Recovery Time Objective, or RTO, is a measure of the users&rsquo; tolerance to down time. The RTO is the amount of time in which a business should be able to restore its systems to a point that will allow it to carry out the impacted operations, even if this is in a limited function.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recovery Point Objective (RPO)</strong> &ndash; The Recovery Point Objective, or RPO, is a measure of how much data loss due to a node failure is acceptable to the business. A large RPO means that the business can tolerate a great deal of lost data; as every business has their own backup routines with some having constant synchronization in place and others with daily, weekly and month backups, data loss could occur when a DS solution has to be implemented to its full effect.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Prepared for Disaster:<br />\r\n<span>Recover faster with Web-Werks</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With a more effective approach : leveraging the power of cloud computing and our proven experience to help you protect and recover your information. DR-as-a-service is designed to help companies to replicate critical servers and Applications to the cloud, so that you can protect your applications and data, and get them back precisely when you need the most.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks has custom-backup solutions specifically designed for various online business operations. We have numerous technologies available each with different type of functionality and back up retention period. Every business is different, to account for this, we offer a range of different software&rsquo;s that will suite backup needs of most business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Web Werks :</strong> Affordable Disaster Recovery solutions (DraaS) minimize exposure to data loss caused by a disaster while reducing total cost of ownership deployed via Cloud Infrastructure. Our low cost disaster recovery solutions help you to overcome potential failures which can cause harm to your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The aim of our business continuity plans is to exclude all single point of failures and ensure you are up and running at all times. With combination of various virtualization and replication technologies, we have built a robust system while keeping your costs low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Understanding our customers means understanding how critical their data is. At Web Werks, data security is a crucial part of our solution and to protect your data during any kind of failures. Our pro-active support team are well trained to handle any disaster recovery situations available round the clock.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Web Werks Data Center Disaster Recovery Solutions</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="inner-list">\r\n	<li><strong>Recovery Time:</strong> Lesser Application Recovery time</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Failover flexibility:</strong> Support for Application Fail-overs and data center recovery.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Frequent Testing: </strong> Flexibility for frequent recovery plan exercising.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Reduced Cost:</strong> Makes disaster recovery affordable through consolidation savings and re-use of existing servers for your DR site.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Reduced Risk: </strong> Reduced recovery risk due to oversubscribed resources limitations following the occurrence of a major disaster event. Simplifies the ability to test thereby enhancing disaster recovery plan reliability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>How do we do it ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li><strong>We provide a menu of replications options</strong> that allows you to continously replicate critical servers into our cloud environment. Leveraging Host-based or Storage-based replications.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pre-build the entire virtual recovery environment</strong> in our cloud data center, including private network connectivity, Security and Fail-Over plans for real-time synchronization.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Expert&rsquo;s support recovery</strong> of your servers, configuring them to run within our cloud environment until you are able to restore your business operations at your primary data center.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Our DRaas data centers are SSAE</strong> 16-complaints, with 2N power redundancy. That means the lights never go out. We&rsquo;ve built them to comply with PCI, SOX and HIPAA requirements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="benefits-block">\r\n                        	<h2>Features</h2>\r\n                            <ul class="benefits-list">\r\n                              <li>Office space with 100% Power Back up</li>\r\n                            <li>Central Air Conditioning space with workstations</li>\r\n                            <li>Basic office productivity software</li>\r\n                            <li>LAN with internet Connectivity</li>\r\n                            </ul>\r\n                        </div>\r\n', 'High-Availability DR Service for Business Continuity', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:03:33', '2014-12-25 15:03:33'),
(27, 'managed-firewall-services', 'Secure Your IT Infra with Cisco Managed Firewalls', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Secure Your IT Infra with<br />\r\n<span>Cisco Managed Firewalls</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stop Data Breaches before they happen.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The cost of dealing with a data breach is soaring. But you can protect your business from the revenue loss, legal liability and network outages of server attacks by putting the right security measures in place before disaster strikes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Hosting managed Cisco Firewall solutions add a solid layer of protection between your mission-critical information and malicious attempts to access it. Our firewalls analyze all incoming and outgoing traffic to block suspicious activity inside and out. Web Werks Hosting network security experts will manage the solution for you, making sure your firewall is set to protect your business without disrupting legitimate traffic. Plus, if you order now, you&rsquo;ll receive 10% off the monthly price for the life of your account and free setup!*</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<p><strong>Cisco ASA 5500 Series Firewall Edition</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Focus on growing your business without worrying about the latest security threats. Cisco ASA 5500 Series firewall editions include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Market-leading firewall technology</li>\r\n	<li>Trusted services to secure modern network environments</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible policies that prevent unauthorized access to network resources</li>\r\n	<li>Easy deployment and day-to-day management features</li>\r\n	<li>Enterprise-class resiliency and scalability options</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Initial setup and configuration</li>\r\n	<li>Setting of rules and policies</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of virtual IP&rsquo;s and NATs</li>\r\n	<li>Firmware maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>User creation</li>\r\n	<li>Rule backup</li>\r\n	<li>Setup and configuration of high availability mode</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Secure Your IT Infra with Cisco Managed Firewalls', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:05:25', '2014-12-25 15:06:07'),
(28, 'backup-storage', 'Backup Storage Solutions', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Backup<br />\r\n<span>Storage Solutions</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Protecting your data from unexpected catastrophes isn&rsquo;t just a good idea &ndash; it&rsquo;s a business necessity. Hardware and system failures, human error and virus infection are but a few of the unanticipated events that can cost thousands of dollars to repair and potentially halt your operations, no matter the size of your business. It&rsquo;s imperative to have a data protection and recovery plan in place so that you never subject your organization to unnecessary risks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks backup solutions protect your critical data, simplify the management of data backup and recovery and provide consistent, reliable and secure data protection. As your business grows and your requirements change, you can cost-effectively upgrade, add options and extend solutions so your needs are always met. Web Werks offers the following backup solutions:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Backup Storage Solutions', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:07:50', '2014-12-25 15:07:50'),
(29, 'managed-load-balancing-services-in-india', 'Load Balancing', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Load <span>Balancing</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s a process and technology that distributes site traffic among several servers using a network-based device. This device intercept traffic destined for a site and deflects that traffic to various servers.A business might decide to assign its workload across a platform for a number of reasons. Speed is a particularly important one, and often the main driver where sites with large traffic are concerned. But introducing a load balancer also makes a platform more stable through its inherent redundancy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our managed load balancing solution sends your traffic through a redundant network of load balancers, distributing your data load between all of your servers. And if one of your servers stop, the others take on its work &ndash; so your users will never find your website down or your services offline. Managed load balancing provides the ultimate availability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As well as managing and maintaining your load balancing services, connectivity and hardware, Web Werks provide 24/7/365 support from our fully trained certified IT experts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Why Web Werks:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Cloud Load Balancers offer a cost-effective and reliable cloud-based failover solution. Easy to set up and manage, our flexible structure grows with your business and ensures you stay responsive to changing needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our load balancing services provide fast connection and breakdown safe 24&times;7 access to web sites and other critical Internet and Intranet applications that help you reduce response time while maximizing site availability. Our load balancing solutions support all Internet protocols and accommodate all operating systems.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li><strong>Maximum Performance:</strong>Improve the performance of yours server farm by running distributed applications where the load balancer forward end-users requests to applications servers based on pre-defined rules &amp; policies.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Increase Scalability:</strong>Load Balancer allows new virtual and /or physical server to be added transparently, maximizing flexibility, and allowing server applications to scale without disruption.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Reliable:</strong>Highly reliable, self-monitoring solutions that manages your application traffic and makes decision about where to route it. Route traffic based on closest servers to reduce latency.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Load Balancing', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:09:30', '2014-12-25 15:09:30'),
(30, 'global-traffic-director', 'Global Traffic Director Services by Web Werks', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Global Traffic Director Services<br />\r\n<span>by Web Werks</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Global Traffic Director from Web Werks provides geographical source-based IP routing which allows the administrator to optimize traffic flow based on the geographical location of the end user.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Traffic can be regionally divided among different servers or data centers which can greatly increase the performance of DNS by segmenting traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Global Traffic Director service uses an AnyCast network to identify the geographical location of the querying client and allow the administrator to define a specific route to a specific server regionally. It is useful is you have multiple different servers located around the world and you want to direct a specific query to the closest server. For example, direct your clients in Europe to a European cloud while directing clients in the United States to a cloud in the United States. This traffic management is done in real time with Instant DNS Updates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Combining Global Traffic Director with additional services such as Load Balancing services will allow a network administrator to optimize network performance while also ensuring availability and redundancy of network nodes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Traffic Segmentation</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>US-East</li>\r\n	<li>US-West</li>\r\n	<li>Europe</li>\r\n	<li>Asia</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection ">\r\n<h2 class="title-inner">Pricing</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Global Traffic Director service is priced per domain per year added onto our DataCenter Services. You must have services with us to avail of Global Traffic Director. Please contact sales@webwerks.com for more information or Call us now.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Geographically distributed query response &ndash; optimized performance for DNS</li>\r\n	<li>Network administrators can build a multi-tiered load balancing and DNS Failover solution in conjunction with the Global Traffic Director.</li>\r\n	<li>Redirect traffic around problem network nodes or outages.</li>\r\n	<li>Segment global traffic for faster access to cloud and data services.</li>\r\n	<li>No additional hardware or software required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Global Traffic Director Services by Web Werks', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:16:33', '2014-12-25 15:16:33'),
(31, 'content-delivery-network-service-provider-in-india', 'What is a Content Delivery Network? ', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h4 class="title-inner">What is a Content Delivery Network?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>A Content Delivery Network (CDN) ensures your customers and visitors spend less time waiting on content &ndash; reducing lost opportunities and lost sales. CDNs store a copy of your web content on local servers, which can be defined by city, country and every continent worldwide &ndash; so your visitors get your content from the closest possible location.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks allows you to use as many of these locations as you like, to accelerate all kinds of web content such as static and dynamic pages, images, audio, video and file downloads.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection ">\r\n<h4 class="title-inner">How can I customize?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Building your custom Content Delivery Network is easy, select your estimated monthly usage, choose the locations that matter to you, tell us how much you&rsquo;re willing to spend, define what sort of quality you need, and we&rsquo;ll tell you how long it&rsquo;ll last. Or if you&rsquo;re not sure just launch our global package, and refine it as you analyze the results.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-style-single">\r\n	<li>Location</li>\r\n	<li>Price</li>\r\n	<li>Time</li>\r\n	<li>Quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="innersection ">\r\n<h4 class="title-inner">How do I get it?</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact <strong>Sales@webwerks.com</strong> for more information and Pricing</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul class="benefits-list">\r\n	<li>Better web performance creates a better experience for your customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Increase click-throughs, conversions, sales and repeat visits.</li>\r\n	<li>Make your site more scalable and resilient without huge expense.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="benefits-block">\r\n<h2 style="background:none; padding-left:0px;">What makes Web Werk&rsquo;s CDN different?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;ve ever considered implementing a Content Delivery Network, it was probably a frustrating experience. If you try to buy a Content Delivery Network &lsquo;out the box&rsquo; you can expect to pay exorbitant fee to a big service provider. It&rsquo;s usually a one-size fits all model, resulting in you paying for resources you don&rsquo;t need or are nowhere near your audience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'What is a Content Delivery Network? ', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 15:18:39', '2014-12-25 15:18:39'),
(32, 'infrastructure', 'Web Werks DC Virtual Tour', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<h1 class="title-inner">Web Werks<br />\r\n<span>DC Virtual Tour</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>COMING SOON</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', 'Web Werks DC Virtual Tour', '', '', 0, '2014-12-25 16:32:10', '2014-12-25 16:32:10'),
(33, 'about-web-werks', 'About webwerks', NULL, '<div class="leftCol">\r\n<div class="innersection iborder-btm">\r\n<p>For more than a decade, Web Werks had helped companies build and manage profitable online business. We offer a complete solutions: world-class e-commerce websites, back-end order management system, e-commerce expertise, online marketing, web hosting &amp; websites development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks, started in the year 1996, and is recognized as one of the fastest growing and most experienced Web Hosting and Web Development Company. While we have successfully delivered numerous projects in the areas of Web Hosting, Data Center Services, Web designing, Online application development, Search Engine Optimization, Internet Marketing, Digital Marketing, Online Branding, E-commerce Solutions, and Mobile Application Development, we have also gathered vast knowledge base through continuous innovation and learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our corporate office in Mumbai boasts a team of over 350 professionals working in a state of the art Development Center. We have expanded our development team and data center in Pune, India. This has been planned in to create a larger skill and infrastructure base for our clients in India and abroad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks has worked with more than 1000 organizations across 23 countries and our clientele includes Fortune 500 companies, Multi-national corporations, Government sector and large Indian and Foreign Business houses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks Data Center changes the economics of the data center by unifying compute, storage, networking, virtualization, and management into a single platform. The result is operational simplicity and business agility &mdash; essential for Cloud computing and deploying IT as a service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Werks DC opened in December 2008, at 1200 sq.ft. in size, it provides up to 16 Amps per cabinet location with N+1 redundancy at all times. All India-based servers are deployed in the Data Center